com.thomsonreuters.upa.codec

Interface XMLDecoder

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    AckMsg, Array, CloseMsg, ElementList, FieldList, FilterList, GenericMsg, Map, Msg, PostMsg, RefreshMsg, RequestMsg, Series, StatusMsg, UpdateMsg, Vector

    public interface XMLDecoder
    The UPA XML Decoder. Decodes a container of binary data to XML.
    Note that the container to be decoded must be the next piece of data in line to be decoded before this method is called.
    Calling decodeToXml(DecodeIterator) on the message container decodes all containers within the message to XML.
    See Also:
    DataTypes
